      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is currently not in running order. It will require a full mechanical overhaul, as the engine needs significant repairs and the transmission is slipping. Externally, there is widespread rust on the rocker panels, a cracked windshield, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. This is strictly a parts car or a major restoration project for someone with the right tools and time.",
